OL,3,CBeloved seafront fairground in
OL,4,CPorthcawl to shutdown
OL,6,FPorthcawl's Coney Beach fairground
OL,7,Fwill close its doors for good after
OL,8,Fmore than a century of operation, the
OL,9,Fowners announced on Wednesday (July 9).
OL,11,FIn an emotional Facebook post, the
OL,12,Fowners shared the "heavy-hearted"
OL,13,Fnews, stating, "this season at Coney
OL,14,FBeach will be our last."
OL,16,FThey described the closure as "the end
OL,17,Fof an era," reflecting on how their
OL,18,Ffamily and other showmen had
OL,19,Fcontributed to making Porthcawl a
OL,20,Fvibrant seaside destination for over a
OL,21,Fhundred years.
