OL,3,CBeloved seafront fairground in
OL,4,CPorthcawl to shutdown
OL,6,F"Bringing fun, laughter and fond
OL,7,Fmemories to so many," the post read,
OL,8,Fexpressing gratitude for being part of
OL,9,Fgenerations of families' lives.
OL,11,F"We will miss it greatly and while we
OL,12,Fare sad to see our time here come to
OL,13,Fan end we are forever grateful to have
OL,14,Fhad the opportunity to have been part
OL,15,Fof so many generations of families
OL,16,Flives, young and old.
OL,18,F"Thank you for sharing our love of
OL,19,F'all the fun of the fair' and the
OL,20,Flegacy that Coney Beach leaves."
