OL,3,CBeloved seafront fairground in
OL,4,CPorthcawl to shutdown
OL,6,FThe fairground is thought to have been
OL,7,Foriginally built to entertain troops
OL,8,Freturning from World War I and was
OL,9,Fnamed as a tribute to the famous Coney
OL,10,FIsland amusement park in New York.
OL,12,FConey Beach experienced a significant
OL,13,Fboom in popularity in the 1950s,
OL,14,Fdrawing large crowds with events such
OL,15,Fas boxing matches, firework displays,
OL,16,Fand aerial acrobat shows.
