OL,3,CBeloved seafront fairground in
OL,4,CPorthcawl to shutdown
OL,6,FThe closure paves the way for the
OL,7,FPorthcawl Waterfront Regeneration
OL,8,FProject, a joint initiative by
OL,9,FBridgend Council and the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FThe site is earmarked for significant
OL,13,Fredevelopment, which will include
OL,14,F1,100 new homes, a variety of shops
OL,15,Fand restaurants, and an extension of
OL,16,Fthe town's boardwalks and green spaces.
